desc_short	-----								Click, turn and match four blocks! Enjoy smart and speedy puzzle action! Clickr is a next generation puzzle game developed by Ntreev Soft, the studio behind Pangya & Trickster. The game competed in the 2010 Independent Games Festival and was selected as 'Top 10 Break Out Indie Games of 2010' by DIYGamer.							
